（1）设 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l}x = 1 + t^2,\\ y = \cos t, \end{array} \right.$ 则 $\frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2} = \_$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\1991\按题拆分\真题\第01题\题目.md', '1991\按题拆分\真题\第01题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '1991 真题 第1题 # 一、填空题（本题共5小题，每小题3分，满分15分）

（1）设 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l}x = 1 + t^2,\\ y = \cos t, \end{array} \right.$ 则 $\frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2} = \_$');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_1991_main_q01', 'math1_1991_main_q01', 1991, 1, 1, 1, '(1)【答案】 $\frac{\sin t - t\cos t}{4t^3}$ .

【解】 $\frac{\mathrm{dy}}{\mathrm{dx}} = \frac{\mathrm{dy} / \mathrm{dt}}{\mathrm{dx} / \mathrm{dt}} = \frac{-\sin t}{2t}$

$$
\frac {\mathrm {d} ^ {2} y}{\mathrm {d} x ^ {2}} = \frac {\mathrm {d} \left(\frac {\mathrm {d} y}{\mathrm {d} x}\right)}{\mathrm {d} x} = \frac {\mathrm {d} \left(\frac {\mathrm {d} y}{\mathrm {d} x}\right) / \mathrm {d} t}{\mathrm {d} x / \mathrm {d} t} = - \frac {\frac {2 t \cos t - 2 \sin t}{4 t ^ {2}}}{2 t} = \frac {\sin t - t \cos t}{4 t ^ {3}}.
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\1991\解析\1991年解析.md', 'ok', 'sequential_year_index', 0.098, '1991:1', 11, 0.146);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_1991_main_q02', 'math1', 1991, '真题', 'main', 2, '# 一、填空题（本题共5小题，每小题3分，满分15分）

(2) 由方程 $xyz + \sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2} = \sqrt{2}$ 所确定的函数 $z = z(x, y)$ 在点 $(1, 0, -1)$ 处的全微分 $\mathrm{d}z = \_$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\1991\按题拆分\真题\第02题\题目.md', '1991\按题拆分\真题\第02题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '1991 真题 第2题 # 一、填空题（本题共5小题，每小题3分，满分15分）

(2) 由方程 $xyz + \sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2} = \sqrt{2}$ 所确定的函数 $z = z(x, y)$ 在点 $(1, 0, -1)$ 处的全微分 $\mathrm{d}z = \_$');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_1991_main_q02', 'math1_1991_main_q02', 1991, 2, 2, 2, '(2)【答案】 $\mathrm{d}x - \sqrt{2}\mathrm{d}y$

【解】 方法一

$xyz + \sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2} = \sqrt{2}$ 两边对 $x$ 求偏导得

$$
y z + x y \frac {\partial z}{\partial x} + \frac {x + z \frac {\partial z}{\partial x}}{\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}} = 0, \text {解 得} \frac {\partial z}{\partial x} \Big | _ {(1, 0, - 1)} = 1;
$$

$xyz + \sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2} = \sqrt{2}$ 两边对 $y$ 求偏导得

$$
x z + x y   {\frac {\partial z}{\partial y}} + {\frac {y + z   {\frac {\partial z}{\partial y}}}{\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}}} = 0  , \text {解 得} {\frac {\partial z}{\partial y}}   \Big | _ {(1, 0, - 1)} = - {\sqrt {2}}  ,
$$

故 $\mathrm{d}z|_{(1,0,-1)} = \mathrm{d}x - \sqrt{2}\mathrm{d}y.$

方法二

$x y z + \sqrt{x^{2} + y^{2} + z^{2}} = \sqrt{2}$ 两边求微分得

$$
\mathrm {d} (x y z) + \mathrm {d} (\sqrt {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}}) = 0,
$$

即 $yz \, \mathrm{d}x + xz \, \mathrm{d}y + xy \, \mathrm{d}z + \frac{x \, \mathrm{d}x + y \, \mathrm{d}y + z \, \mathrm{d}z}{\sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}} = 0,$

将 $(x,y,z) = (1,0, - 1)$ 代入得

$$
\mathrm {d} z \mid_ {(1, 0, - 1)} = \mathrm {d} x - \sqrt {2} \mathrm {d} y.
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\1991\解析\1991年解析.md', 'ok', 'sequential_year_index', 0.204, '1991:2', 2, 0.204);
