$\begin{array}{r}a_{22}\qquad a_{23}\\ a_{12}\qquad a_{13}\\ a_{32} + a_{12}\qquad a_{33} + a_{13} \end{array}$ 0 1 0 1 0 0 1

$p_{2} = \left( \begin{array}{lll}1 & 0 & 0\\ 0 & 1 & 0\\ 1 & 0 & 1 \end{array} \right)$ 则必有（ ）.

(a) $\mathbf{a}\mathbf{p}_1\mathbf{p}_2 = \mathbf{b}$

