$$

$$
P \{X = 3, Y = 2 \} = P \{\xi = 3, \eta = 2 \} + P \{\xi = 2, \eta = 3 \} = \frac {2}{9},
$$

$$
P \{X = 3, Y = 3 \} = \frac {1}{9},
$$

故 $(X,Y)$ 的联合分布律为

