(2) 验证 $\pmb{\eta}_{1} = \binom{4}{1}, \pmb{\eta}_{2} = \binom{-1}{1}$ 是 $\pmb{A}$ 的两个线性无关的特征向量, 并求出相应的特征值;', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2000\按题拆分\真题\第20题\题目.md', '2000\按题拆分\真题\第20题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2000 真题 第20题 # 十一、(本题满分8分)

(2) 验证 $\pmb{\eta}_{1} = \binom{4}{1}, \pmb{\eta}_{2} = \binom{-1}{1}$ 是 $\pmb{a}$ 的两个线性无关的特征向量, 并求出相应的特征值;');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2000_main_q20', 'tag_线性代数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2000_main_q20', 'math1_2000_main_q20', 2000, 20, 20, 20, '（20）【解】 随机变量 $X$ 的分布律为

$$
P \{X = k \} = p (1 - p) ^ {k - 1} (k = 1, 2, \dots),
$$

则 $E(X) = \sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}kP\{X = k\} = p\sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}k(1 - p)^{k - 1}.$

令 $S(x) = \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} kx^{k-1}(|x| < 1)$ ，则 $S(x) = \left(\sum_{k=1}^{\infty} x^k\right)'' = \left(\frac{x}{1-x}\right)'' = \frac{1}{(1-x)^2}$ .

于是 $E(X) = pS(1 - p) = \frac{1}{p}; E(X^2) = \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} k^2 P\{X = k\} = p \sum_{k=1}^{\infty} k^2 (1 - p)^{k-1}$ ,

令 $S_{1}(x) = \sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}k^{2}x^{k - 1}$

则 $S_{1}(x) = \sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}k(k - 1)x^{k - 1} + \sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}kx^{k - 1}$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = x \sum_ {k = 2} ^ {\infty} k (k - 1) x ^ {k - 2} + \frac {1}{(1 - x) ^ {2}} = x \left(\sum_ {k = 2} ^ {\infty} x ^ {k}\right) ^ {\prime \prime} + \frac {1}{(1 - x) ^ {2}} \\ = x \left(\frac {x ^ {2}}{1 - x}\right) ^ {\prime \prime} + \frac {1}{(1 - x) ^ {2}} = \frac {1 + x}{(1 - x) ^ {3}}, \\ \end{array}
$$

则 $E(X^{2}) = pS_{1}(1 - p) = \frac{2 - p}{p^{2}}$ 于是 $D(X) = E(X^2) - [E(X)]^2 = \frac{1 - p}{p^2}$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2000\解析\2000年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.027, '2000:20', 19, 0.243);
