(1) 汽锤击打桩 3 次后, 可将桩打进地下多深?', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2003\按题拆分\真题\第18题\题目.md', '2003\按题拆分\真题\第18题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2003 真题 第18题 # 六、(本题满分10分)

(1) 汽锤击打桩 3 次后, 可将桩打进地下多深?');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2003_main_q18', 'math1_2003_main_q18', 2003, 18, 18, 18, '(18)【解】（I） $\iiint_{\Omega(t)} f(x^2 + y^2 + z^2) \, \mathrm{d}v = \int_0^{2\pi} \mathrm{d}\theta \int_0^\pi \mathrm{d}\varphi \int_0^t r^2 \sin \varphi f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r = 4\pi \int_0^t r^2 f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r,$

$$
\begin{array}{l} \iint_ {D (t)} f \left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}\right) d \sigma = \int_ {0} ^ {2 \pi} d \theta \int_ {0} ^ {t} r f \left(r ^ {2}\right) d r = 2 \pi \int_ {0} ^ {t} r f \left(r ^ {2}\right) d r, \\ \int_ {- t} ^ {t} f \left(x ^ {2}\right) \mathrm {d} x = 2 \int_ {0} ^ {t} f \left(x ^ {2}\right) \mathrm {d} x, \\ \end{array}
$$

则 $F(t) = 2\frac{\int_{0}^{t}r^{2}f(r^{2})\mathrm{d}r}{\int_{0}^{t}rf(r^{2})\mathrm{d}r},G(t) = \pi \frac{\int_{0}^{t}rf(r^{2})\mathrm{d}r}{\int_{0}^{t}f(x^{2})\mathrm{d}x}.$

$$
F ^ {\prime} (t) = 2 t f \left(t ^ {2}\right) \frac {t \int_ {0} ^ {t} r f \left(r ^ {2}\right) \mathrm {d} r - \int_ {0} ^ {t} r ^ {2} f \left(r ^ {2}\right) \mathrm {d} r}{\left(\int_ {0} ^ {t} r f \left(r ^ {2}\right) \mathrm {d} r\right) ^ {2}},
$$

令 $\varphi (t) = t\int_{0}^{t}rf(r^{2})\mathrm{d}r - \int_{0}^{t}r^{2}f(r^{2})\mathrm{d}r,\quad \varphi (0) = 0,$

$$
\varphi^ {\prime} (t) = \int_ {0} ^ {t} r f (r ^ {2}) \mathrm {d} r > 0 (t > 0),
$$

由 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} \varphi(0) = 0, \\ \varphi''(t) > 0 (t > 0) \end{array} \right.$ 得 $\varphi(t) > 0 (t > 0)$ ，于是 $F''(t) > 0 (t > 0)$ ，故 $F(t)$ 在 $(0, +\infty)$ 内单调增加.

$\mathrm{I} = \frac{\pi\int_{0}^{t}rf(r^{2})\mathrm{d}r}{\int_{0}^{t}f(r^{2})\mathrm{d}r},$

当 $t > 0$ 时， $F(t) - \frac{2}{\pi} G(t) > 0$ 等价于 $\int_{0}^{t} f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r \int_{0}^{t} r^2 f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r - \left[ \int_{0}^{t} r f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r \right]^2 > 0.$ 令 $h(t) = \int_{0}^{t} f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r \int_{0}^{t} r^2 f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r - \left[ \int_{0}^{t} r f(r^2) \, \mathrm{d}r \right]^2, h(0) = 0,$

$h^{\prime}(t) = f(t^{2})\int_{0}^{t}f(r^{2})(t - r)^{2}\mathrm{d}r$ ，当 $t > 0$ 时， $h^\prime (t) > 0$

由 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l}h(0) = 0,\\ h''(t) > 0(t > 0), \end{array} \right.$ 得 $h(t) > 0(t > 0)$ ，于是 $F(t) > \frac{2}{\pi} G(t)$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2003\解析\2003年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0, '2003:18', 16, 0.208);
