设随机变量 $X$ 与 $Y$ 相互独立， $X$ 的概率分布为 $P\{X = i\} = \frac{1}{3} (i = -1,0,1), Y$ 的概率密度为 $f_{Y}(y) = \begin{cases} 1, & 0 \leqslant y < 1, \\ 0, & \text{其他}, \end{cases}$ 记 $Z = X + Y$ .

(I) 求 $P\left\{Z \leqslant \frac{1}{2} \mid X = 0\right\}$ ;   
（Ⅱ）求 $Z$ 的概率密度 $f_{Z}(z)$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2008\按题拆分\真题\第22题\题目.md', '2008\按题拆分\真题\第22题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2008 真题 第22题 (22) (本题满分 11 分)

设随机变量 $x$ 与 $y$ 相互独立， $x$ 的概率分布为 $p\{x = i\} = \frac{1}{3} (i = -1,0,1), y$ 的概率密度为 $f_{y}(y) = \begin{cases} 1, & 0 \leqslant y < 1, \\ 0, & \text{其他}, \end{cases}$ 记 $z = x + y$ .

(i) 求 $p\left\{z \leqslant \frac{1}{2} \mid x = 0\right\}$ ;   
（ⅱ）求 $z$ 的概率密度 $f_{z}(z)$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2008_main_q22', 'tag_概率');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2008_main_q22', 'math1_2008_main_q22', 2008, 22, 22, 22, '(22)【解】（I） $P\left\{Z \leqslant \frac{1}{2} \mid X = 0\right\} = P\left\{Y \leqslant \frac{1}{2}\right\} = \int_{0}^{\frac{1}{2}} 1 \, \mathrm{d}y = \frac{1}{2}$ .

$(\mathrm{II})F_{Z}(z) = P\{Z\leqslant z\} = P\{X + Y\leqslant z\}$

当 $z < -1$ 时， $F_{Z}(z) = 0$

当 $z \geqslant 2$ 时， $F_{Z}(z) = 1$

当 $-1\leqslant z <   2$ 时，

$$
\begin{array}{l} F _ {Z} (z) = P \{X = - 1 \} \cdot P \{X + Y \leqslant z \mid X = - 1 \} + P \{X = 0 \} \cdot P \{X + Y \leqslant z \mid X = 0 \} + \\ P \{X = 1 \} \cdot P \{X + Y \leqslant z \mid X = 1 \} \\ = \frac {1}{3} P \{Y \leqslant z + 1 \} + \frac {1}{3} P \{Y \leqslant z \} + \frac {1}{3} P \{Y \leqslant z - 1 \}, \\ \end{array}
$$

当 $-1\leqslant z <   0$ 时， $F_{Z}(z) = \frac{1}{3} P\{Y\leqslant z + 1\} = \frac{1}{3}\int_{0}^{z + 1}\mathrm{d}y = \frac{1}{3} (z + 1);$

当 $0 \leqslant z < 1$ 时， $F_{Z}(z) = \frac{1}{3} + \frac{1}{3} P\{Y \leqslant z\} = \frac{1}{3} + \frac{1}{3} \int_{0}^{z} \mathrm{d}y = \frac{1}{3} (z + 1)$

当 $1 \leqslant z < 2$ 时， $F_{Z}(z) = \frac{2}{3} + \frac{1}{3} P\{Y \leqslant z - 1\} = \frac{2}{3} + \frac{1}{3} \int_{0}^{z - 1} \mathrm{d}y = \frac{1}{3} (z + 1)$ ，

从而 $F_{Z}(z) = \left\{ \begin{array}{ll}0, & z < - 1,\\ \frac{1}{3} (z + 1), & -1\leqslant z < 2,\\ 1, & z\geqslant 2. \end{array} \right.$

故 $f_{Z}(z) = \left\{ \begin{array}{ll} \frac{1}{3}, & -1 < z < 2, \\ 0, & \text{其他}. \end{array} \right.$

方法点评：设随机变量 $X$ 为离散型，其分布律为 $P\{X = x_i\} = p_i (i = 1,2,\dots,m)$ ，而随机变量 $Y$ 为连续型，其分布函数为 $f(x)$ ，且 $X, Y$ 独立，求 $Z = X + Y$ 的分布函数时往往使用全概率公式，即

$$
\begin{array}{l} F _ {Z} (z) = P \{Z \leqslant z \} = P \{X + Y \leqslant z \} \\ = P \{X = x _ {1} \} P \{X + Y \leqslant z \mid X = x _ {1} \} + \dots + P \{X = x _ {m} \} P \{X + Y \leqslant z \mid X = x _ {n} \}. \\ \end{array}
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2008\解析\2008年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.154, '2008:22', 22, 0.154);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2008_main_q23', 'math1', 2008, '真题', 'main', 23, '(23) (本题满分 11 分)

设 $X_{1}, X_{2}, \dots, X_{n}$ 是总体 $N(\mu, \sigma^{2})$ 的简单随机样本，记

$$
\bar {X} = \frac {1}{n} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} X _ {i}, \quad S ^ {2} = \frac {1}{n - 1} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} \left(X _ {i} - \bar {X}\right) ^ {2}, \quad T = \bar {X} ^ {2} - \frac {1}{n} S ^ {2}.
$$

(I) 证明 $T$ 是 $\mu^2$ 的无偏估计量；  
（Ⅱ）当 $\mu = 0, \sigma = 1$ 时，求 $D(T)$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2008\按题拆分\真题\第23题\题目.md', '2008\按题拆分\真题\第23题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2008 真题 第23题 (23) (本题满分 11 分)

设 $x_{1}, x_{2}, \dots, x_{n}$ 是总体 $n(\mu, \sigma^{2})$ 的简单随机样本，记

$$
\bar {x} = \frac {1}{n} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} x _ {i}, \quad s ^ {2} = \frac {1}{n - 1} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} \left(x _ {i} - \bar {x}\right) ^ {2}, \quad t = \bar {x} ^ {2} - \frac {1}{n} s ^ {2}.
$$

(i) 证明 $t$ 是 $\mu^2$ 的无偏估计量；  
（ⅱ）当 $\mu = 0, \sigma = 1$ 时，求 $d(t)$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2008_main_q23', 'tag_级数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2008_main_q23', 'math1_2008_main_q23', 2008, 23, 23, 23, '(23)【解】（I）由 $\overline{X} \sim N\left(\mu, \frac{\sigma^2}{n}\right)$ ，得 $E(\overline{X}^2) = D(\overline{X}) + [E(\overline{X})]^2 = \frac{\sigma^2}{n} + \mu^2$

再由 $E(S^2) = \sigma^2$ ，得 $E(T) = E(\overline{X}^2) - \frac{1}{n} E(S^2) = \frac{\sigma^2}{n} +\mu^2 -\frac{\sigma^2}{n} = \mu^2.$

于是 $T = \overline{X}^2 -\frac{1}{n} S^2$ 为 $\mu^2$ 的无偏估计量.

（Ⅱ）当 $\mu = 0, \sigma = 1$ 时， $\overline{X} \sim N\left(0, \frac{1}{n}\right)$ ，标准化得 $\sqrt{n}\overline{X} \sim N(0,1)$ ，于是 $n\overline{X}^2 \sim \chi^2(1)$

又 $\frac{(n - 1)S^2}{\sigma^2} = (n - 1)S^2 \sim \chi^2(n - 1)$ ，且 $\overline{X}$ 与 $S^2$ 独立，得

$$
\begin{array}{l} D (T) = D \left(\bar {X} ^ {2}\right) + \frac {1}{n ^ {2}} D \left(S ^ {2}\right) = \frac {1}{n ^ {2}} D \left(n \bar {X} ^ {2}\right) + \frac {1}{n ^ {2} (n - 1) ^ {2}} D [ (n - 1) S ^ {2} ] \\ = \frac {2}{n ^ {2}} + \frac {2 (n - 1)}{n ^ {2} (n - 1) ^ {2}} = \frac {2}{n ^ {2}} + \frac {2}{n ^ {2} (n - 1)} = \frac {2}{n (n - 1)}. \\ \end{array}
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2008\解析\2008年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.229, '2008:23', 23, 0.229);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2009_main_q01', 'math1', 2009, '真题', 'main', 1, '(1) 当 $x \to 0$ 时, $f(x) = x - \sin ax$ 与 $g(x) = x^2 \ln (1 - bx)$ 是等价无穷小量, 则( )

(A) $a = 1, b = -\frac{1}{6}$ .

(B) $a = 1, b = \frac{1}{6}$ .

(C) $a = -1, b = -\frac{1}{6}$ .

(D) $a = -1, b = \frac{1}{6}$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2009\按题拆分\真题\第01题\题目.md', '2009\按题拆分\真题\第01题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2009 真题 第1题 (1) 当 $x \to 0$ 时, $f(x) = x - \sin ax$ 与 $g(x) = x^2 \ln (1 - bx)$ 是等价无穷小量, 则( )

(a) $a = 1, b = -\frac{1}{6}$ .

(b) $a = 1, b = \frac{1}{6}$ .

(c) $a = -1, b = -\frac{1}{6}$ .

(d) $a = -1, b = \frac{1}{6}$ .');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2009_main_q01', 'math1_2009_main_q01', 2009, 1, 1, 1, '（1）【答案】 （A）.

【解】方法一 $g(x) = x^{2}\ln (1 - bx)\sim -bx^{3},$

$$
f (x) = x - \sin a x = (1 - a) x + \frac {a ^ {3}}{3 !} x ^ {3} + o \left(x ^ {3}\right),
$$

由 $f(x)\sim g(x)$ ，得 $a = 1,b = -\frac{1}{6}$ ，应选(A).

方法二 由 $\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{f(x)}{g(x)} = \lim_{x\to 0}\frac{x - \sin ax}{x^2\ln(1 - bx)} = -\frac{1}{b}\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{x - \sin ax}{x^3} = -\frac{1}{b}\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{1 - a\cos ax}{3x^2} = 1,$

得 $a = 1$

再由 $\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{f(x)}{g(x)} = -\frac{1}{b}\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{1 - \cos x}{3x^2} = -\frac{1}{6b} = 1$ ，得 $b = -\frac{1}{6}$ ，应选(A).

方法三 $g(x)\sim -bx^3$ ，显然 $a = 1$ ，且 $f(x) = x - \sin x\sim \frac{1}{6} x^3$

再由 $f(x)\sim g(x)$ 得 $b = -\frac{1}{6}$ ，应选(A).', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2009\解析\2009年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.308, '2009:1', 1, 0.308);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2009_main_q02', 'math1', 2009, '真题', 'main', 2, '(2)如图，正方形 $\{(x,y)\mid |x|\leqslant 1,|y|\leqslant 1\}$ 被其对角线划分为四个区域 $D_{k}(k = 1,2,3,4),I_{k} = \iint_{D_{k}}y\cos x\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y$ ，则 $\max_{1\leqslant k\leqslant 4}\left\{I_k\right\} = (\quad)$

(A) $I_{1}$ .

(B) $I_{2}$ .

(C) $I_{3}$ .

(D) $I_{4}$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2009\按题拆分\真题\第02题\题目.md', '2009\按题拆分\真题\第02题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2009 真题 第2题 (2)如图，正方形 $\{(x,y)\mid |x|\leqslant 1,|y|\leqslant 1\}$ 被其对角线划分为四个区域 $d_{k}(k = 1,2,3,4),i_{k} = \iint_{d_{k}}y\cos x\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y$ ，则 $\max_{1\leqslant k\leqslant 4}\left\{i_k\right\} = (\quad)$

(a) $i_{1}$ .

(b) $i_{2}$ .

(c) $i_{3}$ .

(d) $i_{4}$ .');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2009_main_q02', 'math1_2009_main_q02', 2009, 2, 2, 2, '（2）【答案】 （A）.

【解】 由 $I_{1} = \iint_{D_{1}}y\cos x\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y = 2\int_{0}^{1}\cos x\mathrm{d}x\int_{x}^{1}y\mathrm{d}y$

$$
= \int_ {0} ^ {1} (1 - x ^ {2}) \cos x \mathrm {d} x > 0,
$$

$$
\begin{array}{l} I _ {2} = \iint_ {D _ {2}} y \cos x \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y = 0, \\ I _ {3} = \iint_ {D _ {3}} y \cos x d x d y = 2 \int_ {0} ^ {1} \cos x d x \int_ {- 1} ^ {- x} y d y = \int_ {0} ^ {1} (x ^ {2} - 1) \cos x d x <   0, \\ I _ {4} = \iint_ {D _ {4}} y \cos x \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y = 0 \text {, 应 选 (A)}. \\ \end{array}
$$

![](images/4bedb164956b9fa2a1e6db7d813c85e8316a8674fd12184fead0bdf9b24d47b4.jpg)  
一（2）题图

方法点评：二重积分的对称性是考查的一个重点，关于对称性有：

（1）设 $D$ 关于 $y$ 轴对称，位于 $y$ 轴右侧的部分为 $D_{1}$ ，则

当 $f(-x,y) = -f(x,y)$ 时 $\iint_{D} f(x,y) \, \mathrm{d}\sigma = 0$ ;

当 $f(-x,y) = f(x,y)$ 时 $\iint_{D}f(x,y)\mathrm{d}\sigma = 2\iint_{D_1}f(x,y)\mathrm{d}\sigma .$

（2）设 $D$ 关于 $\mathcal{X}$ 轴对称，位于 $\mathcal{X}$ 轴上侧的部分为 $D_{1}$ ，则

当 $f(x, -y) = -f(x, y)$ 时 $\iint_{D} f(x, y) \mathrm{d}\sigma = 0$ ;

当 $f(x, -y) = f(x, y)$ 时 $\iint_{D} f(x, y) \mathrm{d}\sigma = 2\iint_{D_1} f(x, y) \mathrm{d}\sigma.$

(3) 当 $D$ 关于 $y = x$ 对称时, $\iint_{D} f(x, y) \, \mathrm{d}x \, \mathrm{d}y = \iint_{D} f(y, x) \, \mathrm{d}x \, \mathrm{d}y$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2009\解析\2009年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.107, '2009:2', 2, 0.107);
