【解】 $\lim_{x\to \infty}\left[\frac{x^2}{(x - a)(x + b)}\right]^x = \lim_{x\to \infty}\left\{\left[1 + \frac{(a - b)x + ab}{(x - a)(x + b)}\right]^{\frac{(x - a)(x + b)}{(a - b)x + ab}}\right\}^{\frac{x[(a - b)x + ab]}{(x - a)(x + b)}} = \mathrm{e}^{a - b},$

应选(C).', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.381, '2010:1', 1, 0.381);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q02', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 2, '(2) 设函数 $z = z(x, y)$ 由方程 $F\left(\frac{y}{x}, \frac{z}{x}\right) = 0$ 确定，其中 $F$ 为可微函数，且 $F_{2}^{\prime} \neq 0$ ，则 $x \frac{\partial z}{\partial x} + y \frac{\partial z}{\partial y} =$ （）

(A) $x$

(B) $z$

(C) $-x$ .

(D) $-z$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第02题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第02题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第2题 (2) 设函数 $z = z(x, y)$ 由方程 $f\left(\frac{y}{x}, \frac{z}{x}\right) = 0$ 确定，其中 $f$ 为可微函数，且 $f_{2}^{\prime} \neq 0$ ，则 $x \frac{\partial z}{\partial x} + y \frac{\partial z}{\partial y} =$ （）

(a) $x$

(b) $z$

(c) $-x$ .

(d) $-z$ .');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q02', 'math1_2010_main_q02', 2010, 2, 2, 2, '(2)【答案】 (B).

【解】 方法一 复合函数求导法则

$F\left(\frac{y}{x}, \frac{z}{x}\right) = 0$ 两边对 $x$ 求偏导，得 $-\frac{y}{x^2} F_1'' + \frac{x \frac{\partial z}{\partial x} - z}{x^2} F_2'' = 0$ ，解得 $\frac{\partial z}{\partial x} = \frac{1}{x F_2''} (y F_1'' + z F_2'')$

$F\left(\frac{y}{x}, \frac{z}{x}\right) = 0$ 两边对 $y$ 求偏导，得 $\frac{1}{x} F_{1}'' + \frac{1}{x} F_{2}'' \frac{\partial z}{\partial y} = 0$ ，解得 $\frac{\partial z}{\partial y} = -\frac{F_{1}''}{F_{2}''}.$

于是 $x\frac{\partial z}{\partial x} +y\frac{\partial z}{\partial y} = \frac{1}{F_2''} (yF_1'' + zF_2'') - \frac{yF_1''}{F_2''} = z$ ，应选(B).

方法二 公式法

令 $G(x,y,z) = F\left(\frac{y}{x},\frac{z}{x}\right)$

由 $G_{x}^{\prime} = -\frac{y}{x^{2}} F_{1}^{\prime} - \frac{z}{x^{2}} F_{2}^{\prime}$ ， $G_{y}^{\prime} = \frac{1}{x} F_{1}^{\prime}$ ， $G_{z}^{\prime} = \frac{1}{x} F_{2}^{\prime}$ ，得

$$
\frac {\partial z}{\partial x} = - \frac {G _ {x} ^ {\prime}}{G _ {z} ^ {\prime}} = \frac {\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} F _ {1} ^ {\prime} + \frac {z}{x ^ {2}} F _ {2} ^ {\prime}}{\frac {1}{x} F _ {2} ^ {\prime}} = \frac {1}{x F _ {2} ^ {\prime}} (y F _ {1} ^ {\prime} + z F _ {2} ^ {\prime}), \quad \frac {\partial z}{\partial y} = - \frac {G _ {y} ^ {\prime}}{G _ {z} ^ {\prime}} = - \frac {\frac {1}{x} F _ {1} ^ {\prime}}{\frac {1}{x} F _ {2} ^ {\prime}} = - \frac {F _ {1} ^ {\prime}}{F _ {2} ^ {\prime}},
$$

于是 $x\frac{\partial z}{\partial x} +y\frac{\partial z}{\partial y} = \frac{1}{F_2''} (yF_1'' + zF_2'') - \frac{yF_1''}{F_2''} = z$ ，应选(B).

方法三 全微分法

$F\left(\frac{y}{x}, \frac{z}{x}\right) = 0$ 两边求全微分，得 $F_{1}^{\prime} \mathrm{d}\left(\frac{y}{x}\right) + F_{2}^{\prime} \mathrm{d}\left(\frac{z}{x}\right) = 0$ ，整理得

$$
F _ {1} ^ {\prime} \cdot \frac {x \mathrm {d} y - y \mathrm {d} x}{x ^ {2}} + F _ {2} ^ {\prime} \cdot \frac {x \mathrm {d} z - z \mathrm {d} x}{x ^ {2}} = 0,
$$

从而有 $\mathrm{d}z = \frac{1}{xF_2''} (yF_1'' + zF_2'')\mathrm{d}x - \frac{F_1''}{F_2''}\mathrm{d}y,$

于是 $\frac{\partial z}{\partial x} = \frac{1}{xF_2''} (yF_1'' + zF_2'')$ ， $\frac{\partial z}{\partial y} = -\frac{F_1''}{F_2''}$

故 $x\frac{\partial z}{\partial x} +y\frac{\partial z}{\partial y} = \frac{1}{F_2''} (yF_1'' + zF_2'') - \frac{yF_1''}{F_2''} = z$ ，应选(B).', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.214, '2010:2', 2, 0.214);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q03', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 3, '(3) 设 $m, n$ 均是正整数，则反常积分 $\int_{0}^{1} \frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^2(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}} \mathrm{d}x$ 的收敛性（ ）

(A) 仅与 $m$ 的取值有关.

(B) 仅与 $n$ 的取值有关.

(C) 与 $m, n$ 的取值都有关.

(D)与 $m,n$ 的取值都无关', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第03题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第03题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第3题 (3) 设 $m, n$ 均是正整数，则反常积分 $\int_{0}^{1} \frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^2(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}} \mathrm{d}x$ 的收敛性（ ）

(a) 仅与 $m$ 的取值有关.

(b) 仅与 $n$ 的取值有关.

(c) 与 $m, n$ 的取值都有关.

(d)与 $m,n$ 的取值都无关');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q03', 'tag_积分');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q03', 'math1_2010_main_q03', 2010, 3, 3, 3, '(3)【答案】 (D).

【解】 $x = 0$ 及 $x = 1$ 为反常积分 $\int_0^1\frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^2(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}}\mathrm{d}x$ 的瑕点，

$$
\int_ {0} ^ {1} \frac {\sqrt [ m ]{\ln^ {2} (1 - x)}}{\sqrt [ n ]{x}} d x = \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {1}{2}} \frac {\sqrt [ m ]{\ln^ {2} (1 - x)}}{\sqrt [ n ]{x}} d x + \int_ {\frac {1}{2}} ^ {1} \frac {\sqrt [ m ]{\ln^ {2} (1 - x)}}{\sqrt [ n ]{x}} d x,
$$

因为 $\lim_{x\to 0^{+}}x^{\frac{1}{n} -\frac{2}{m}}\cdot \frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^{2}(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}} = 1$ 且 $\alpha = \frac{1}{n} -\frac{2}{m} <  1$ ，所以 $\int_0^{\frac{1}{2}}\frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^2(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}}\mathrm{d}x$ 收敛；

又因为 $\lim_{x\to 1^{-}}(1 - x)^{\frac{1}{2}}\cdot \frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^{2}(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}} = \lim_{x\to 1^{-}}\sqrt{1 - x}\cdot \ln^{\frac{2}{m}}(1 - x)$

$$
\underline {{\underline {{1 - x = t}}}} \lim  _ {t \rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \frac {\ln^ {\frac {2}{m}} t}{t ^ {- \frac {1}{2}}} = \left(\lim  _ {t \rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \frac {\ln t}{t ^ {- \frac {m}{4}}}\right) ^ {\frac {2}{m}} = \left(- \frac {4}{m} \lim  _ {t \rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \frac {\frac {1}{t}}{t ^ {- \frac {m}{4} - 1}}\right) ^ {\frac {2}{m}} = 0
$$

且 $\alpha = \frac{1}{2} < 1$ ，所以 $\int_{\frac{1}{2}}^{1}\frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^2(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}}\mathrm{d}x$ 收敛，故 $\int_0^1\frac{\sqrt[m]{\ln^2(1 - x)}}{\sqrt[n]{x}}\mathrm{d}x$ 收敛，应选(D).

方法点评：对积分区间有限但函数有无穷间断点的反常积分的敛散性判断通常有定义法和判别法.

（1）设 $f(x)\in C(a,b]$ ，且 $f(x)$ 在 $x = a$ 的右邻域内无界.

定义法：对任意的 $\varepsilon >0$ ，若 $\lim_{\varepsilon \to 0^{+}}\int_{a + \varepsilon}^{b}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 存在，则称反常积分 $\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 收敛，否则称为发散.

判别法：设 $\lim_{x\to a^{+}}(x - a)^{k}f(x) = A(\neq \infty)$ ，则当 $0 < k < 1, 0 \leqslant A < +\infty$ 时，反常积分 $\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 收敛；当 $k \geqslant 1, 0 < A \leqslant +\infty$ 时，反常积分 $\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 发散.

（2）设 $f(x)\in C[a,b)$ ，且 $f(x)$ 在 $x = b$ 的左邻域内无界.

定义法：对任意的 $\varepsilon >0$ ，若 $\lim_{\varepsilon \to 0^{+}}\int_{a}^{b - \varepsilon}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 存在，则称反常积分 $\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 收敛，否则称为发散.

判别法：设 $\lim_{x\to b^{-}}(b - x)^{k}f(x) = A(\neq \infty)$ ，则当 $0 < k < 1, 0 \leqslant A < +\infty$ 时，反常积分 $\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 收敛；当 $k \geqslant 1, 0 < A \leqslant +\infty$ 时，反常积分 $\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\mathrm{d}x$ 发散.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.241, '2010:3', 3, 0.241);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q04', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 4, '(4) $\lim_{n\to \infty}\sum_{i = 1}^{n}\sum_{j = 1}^{n}\frac{n}{(n + i)(n^2 + j^2)} = (\quad)$

(A) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^x\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y^2)}\mathrm{d}y.$

(B) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^x\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y)}\mathrm{d}y.$

(C) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^1\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y)}\mathrm{d}y.$

(D) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^1\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y^2)}\mathrm{d}y.$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第04题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第04题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第4题 (4) $\lim_{n\to \infty}\sum_{i = 1}^{n}\sum_{j = 1}^{n}\frac{n}{(n + i)(n^2 + j^2)} = (\quad)$

(a) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^x\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y^2)}\mathrm{d}y.$

(b) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^x\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y)}\mathrm{d}y.$

(c) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^1\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y)}\mathrm{d}y.$

(d) $\int_0^1\mathrm{d}x\int_0^1\frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y^2)}\mathrm{d}y.$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q04', 'tag_极限');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q04', 'tag_积分');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q04', 'tag_级数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q04', 'math1_2010_main_q04', 2010, 4, 4, 4, '（4）【答案】 (D).

【解】取 $D = \{(x,y) \mid 0 \leqslant x \leqslant 1, 0 \leqslant y \leqslant 1\}$ , $f(x,y) = \frac{1}{(1 + x)(1 + y^2)}$

由 $\sum_{i=1}^{n}\sum_{j=1}^{n}\frac{n}{(n+i)(n^2+j^2)}=\frac{1}{n^2}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\sum_{j=1}^{n}\frac{1}{\left(1+\frac{i}{n}\right)\left[1+\left(\frac{j}{n}\right)^2\right]}$ , 根据二重积分的定义, 得

$$
\lim  _ {n \rightarrow \infty} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} \sum_ {j = 1} ^ {n} \frac {n}{(n + i) (n ^ {2} + j ^ {2})} = \iint_ {D} f (x, y) d x d y = \int_ {0} ^ {1} d x \int_ {0} ^ {1} \frac {1}{(1 + x) (1 + y ^ {2})} d y,
$$

应选(D).

方法点评：用定积分、重积分等的定义求极限是极限计算的一种重要类型，重点考查定积分定义求极限.

（1）定积分的定义求极限： $\lim_{n\to \infty}\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i = 1}^{n}f\left(\frac{i}{n}\right) = \int_{0}^{1}f(x)\mathrm{d}x.$

【例】 求极限 $\lim_{n\to \infty}\left(\frac{1}{1 + \sqrt{n^2 - 1^2}} +\frac{1}{2 + \sqrt{n^2 - 2^2}} +\dots +\frac{1}{n + \sqrt{n^2 - n^2}}\right)$

【解】 $\lim_{n\to \infty}\left(\frac{1}{1 + \sqrt{n^2 - 1^2}} +\frac{1}{2 + \sqrt{n^2 - 2^2}} +\dots +\frac{1}{n + \sqrt{n^2 - n^2}}\right)$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = \lim  _ {n \rightarrow \infty} \frac {1}{n} \left[ \frac {1}{\frac {1}{n} + \sqrt {1 - \left(\frac {1}{n}\right) ^ {2}}} + \frac {1}{\frac {2}{n} + \sqrt {1 - \left(\frac {2}{n}\right) ^ {2}}} + \dots + \frac {1}{\frac {n}{n} + \sqrt {1 - \left(\frac {n}{n}\right) ^ {2}}} \right] \\ = \lim  _ {n \rightarrow \infty} \frac {1}{n} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} \frac {1}{\frac {i}{n} + \sqrt {1 - \left(\frac {i}{n}\right) ^ {2}}} = \int_ {0} ^ {1} \frac {1}{x + \sqrt {1 - x ^ {2}}} d x \frac {x = \sin t}{\sin t + \cos t} \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {\pi}{2}} \frac {\cos t}{\sin t + \cos t} d t \\ = \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {\pi}{2}} \frac {\cos x}{\sin x + \cos x} d x \xlongequal {x + t = \frac {\pi}{2}} \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {\pi}{2}} \frac {\sin t}{\sin t + \cos t} d t = \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {\pi}{2}} \frac {\sin x}{\sin x + \cos x} d x, \\ \end{array}
$$

于是原式 $= \frac{1}{2}\left(\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}}\frac{\sin x}{\sin x + \cos x}\mathrm{d}x + \int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}}\frac{\cos x}{\sin x + \cos x}\mathrm{d}x\right) = \frac{\pi}{4}.$

(2) 二重积分的定义求极限: $\lim_{\substack{m \to \infty \\ n \to \infty}} \frac{1}{mn} \sum_{i=1}^{m} \sum_{j=1}^{n} f\left(\frac{i}{m}, \frac{j}{n}\right) = \iint_{D} f(x, y) \, \mathrm{d}x \, \mathrm{d}y,$

其中 $D = \{(x,y)\mid 0\leqslant x\leqslant 1,0\leqslant y\leqslant 1\}$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.595, '2010:4', 4, 0.595);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q05', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 5, '(5) 设 $A$ 为 $m \times n$ 矩阵, $B$ 为 $n \times m$ 矩阵, $E$ 为 $m$ 阶单位矩阵, 若 $AB = E$ , 则( )

(A) 秩 $r(\mathbf{A}) = m$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{B}) = m$ .

(B) 秩 $r(\mathbf{A}) = m$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{B}) = n$ .

(C) 秩 $r(\mathbf{A}) = n$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{B}) = m$ .

(D) 秩 $r(\mathbf{A}) = n$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{B}) = n$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第05题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第05题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第5题 (5) 设 $a$ 为 $m \times n$ 矩阵, $b$ 为 $n \times m$ 矩阵, $e$ 为 $m$ 阶单位矩阵, 若 $ab = e$ , 则( )

(a) 秩 $r(\mathbf{a}) = m$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{b}) = m$ .

(b) 秩 $r(\mathbf{a}) = m$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{b}) = n$ .

(c) 秩 $r(\mathbf{a}) = n$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{b}) = m$ .

(d) 秩 $r(\mathbf{a}) = n$ ，秩 $r(\mathbf{b}) = n$ .');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q05', 'tag_线性代数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q05', 'math1_2010_main_q05', 2010, 5, 5, 5, '（5）【答案】 （A）.

【解】 $r(\mathbf{AB}) = r(\mathbf{E}) = m$

因为 $r(\mathbf{AB}) \leqslant r(\mathbf{A})$ 且 $r(\mathbf{AB}) \leqslant r(\mathbf{B})$ ，所以 $r(\mathbf{A}) \geqslant m, r(\mathbf{B}) \geqslant m$ .

又显然 $r(\mathbf{A})\leqslant m,r(\mathbf{B})\leqslant m$ ，故 $r(A) = r(B) = m$ ，应选（A）.

方法点评：本题使用矩阵秩的两个性质：

(1) $r(\mathbf{AB}) \leqslant \min \{r(\mathbf{A}), r(\mathbf{B})\}$ , 研究矩阵秩的时候, 如果出现矩阵的积, 使用此性质;  
（2）设 $\mathbf{A}$ 为 $m\times n$ 矩阵，则 $r(A)\leqslant \min \{m,n\}$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.149, '2010:5', 5, 0.149);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q06', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 6, '(6) 设 $A$ 为4阶实对称矩阵，且 $A^2 + A = O$ . 若 $A$ 的秩为3，则 $A$ 相似于（）

(A) $\left( \begin{array}{cccc}1 & & & \\ & 1 & & \\ & & 1 & \\ & & & 0 \end{array} \right)$ .

(B) $\left( \begin{array}{cccc}1 & & & \\ & 1 & & \\ & & -1 & \\ & & & 0 \end{array} \right).$

( C ) $\left( \begin{array} { c c c c } { 1 } & & & \\ & { - 1 } & & \\ & & { - 1 } & \\ & & & { 0 } \end{array} \right)$

$\left( \begin{array}{rrrr} - 1 & & & \\ & -1 & & \\ & & -1 & \\ & & & 0 \end{array} \right).$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第06题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第06题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第6题 (6) 设 $a$ 为4阶实对称矩阵，且 $a^2 + a = o$ . 若 $a$ 的秩为3，则 $a$ 相似于（）

(a) $\left( \begin{array}{cccc}1 & & & \\ & 1 & & \\ & & 1 & \\ & & & 0 \end{array} \right)$ .

(b) $\left( \begin{array}{cccc}1 & & & \\ & 1 & & \\ & & -1 & \\ & & & 0 \end{array} \right).$

( c ) $\left( \begin{array} { c c c c } { 1 } & & & \\ & { - 1 } & & \\ & & { - 1 } & \\ & & & { 0 } \end{array} \right)$

$\left( \begin{array}{rrrr} - 1 & & & \\ & -1 & & \\ & & -1 & \\ & & & 0 \end{array} \right).$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q06', 'tag_线性代数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q06', 'math1_2010_main_q06', 2010, 6, 6, 6, '（6）【答案】 (D).

【解】令 $AX = \lambda X(X\neq 0)$ ，由 $(A^2 +A)X = (\lambda^2 +\lambda)X = 0$ 且 $X\neq 0$ 得 $\lambda^2 +\lambda = 0$ ，于是 $\lambda = 0$ 或 $\lambda = -1.$ 因为 $\mathbf{A}$ 可对角化且 $r(A) = 3$ ，所以 $\lambda = -1$ 为三重特征值，

故 $\mathbf{A}\sim \left( \begin{array}{rrr} - 1 & & \\ & -1 & \\ & & -1 \end{array} \right),$ 应选(D).', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.212, '2010:6', 20, 0.365);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q07', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 7, '(7) 设随机变量 $X$ 的分布函数 $F(x) = \left\{ \begin{array}{ll} 0, & x < 0, \\ \frac{1}{2}, & 0 \leqslant x < 1, \\ 1 - \mathrm{e}^{-x}, & x \geqslant 1, \end{array} \right.$ 则 $P\{X = 1\} = (\quad)$

(A)0.

(B) $\frac{1}{2}$ .

(C) $\frac{1}{2} - \mathrm{e}^{-1}$ .

(D) $1 - \mathrm{e}^{-1}$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第07题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第07题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第7题 (7) 设随机变量 $x$ 的分布函数 $f(x) = \left\{ \begin{array}{ll} 0, & x < 0, \\ \frac{1}{2}, & 0 \leqslant x < 1, \\ 1 - \mathrm{e}^{-x}, & x \geqslant 1, \end{array} \right.$ 则 $p\{x = 1\} = (\quad)$

(a)0.

(b) $\frac{1}{2}$ .

(c) $\frac{1}{2} - \mathrm{e}^{-1}$ .

(d) $1 - \mathrm{e}^{-1}$ .');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q07', 'tag_概率');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q07', 'math1_2010_main_q07', 2010, 7, 7, 7, '（7）【答案】 (C).

【解】 $P\{X = 1\} = P\{X \leqslant 1\} - P\{X < 1\} = F(1) - F(1 - 0) = 1 - \mathrm{e}^{-1} - \frac{1}{2} = \frac{1}{2} - \mathrm{e}^{-1},$

应选(C).

方法点评：本题需要熟练掌握随机变量分布函数的性质，

设 $X$ 为随机变量， $F(x)$ 具有如下四个特征：

(1) $0 \leqslant F(x) \leqslant 1$   
(2) $F(x)$ 单调不减；  
(3) $F(x)$ 右连续；  
(4) $F(-\infty) = 0$ ， $F(+\infty) = 1$

反之，若 $F(x)$ 具有 $(1) \sim (4)$ 的特征，则 $F(x)$ 为分布函数.

另外，若 $F(x)$ 为分布函数，则

(1) $P\{X < a\} = F(a - 0)$   
(2) $P\{X = a\} = P\{X \leqslant a\} - \{X < a\} = F(a) - F(a - 0)$ ;   
(3) $P\{a < X \leqslant b\} = P\{X \leqslant b\} - P\{X \leqslant a\} = F(b) - F(a)$ ;   
(4) $P\{a < X < b\} = P\{X < b\} - P\{X \leqslant a\} = F(b - 0) - F(a)$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.157, '2010:7', 14, 0.196);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q08', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 8, '(8) 设 $f_{1}(x)$ 为标准正态分布的概率密度, $f_{2}(x)$ 为 $[-1,3]$ 上均匀分布的概率密度, 若

$$
f (x) = \left\{ \begin{array}{l l} a f _ {1} (x), & x \leqslant 0, \\ b f _ {2} (x), & x > 0 \end{array} \right. (a > 0, b > 0)
$$

为概率密度, 则 $a, b$ 应满足( )

(A) $2a + 3b = 4$

(B) $3a + 2b = 4$

(C) $a + b = 1$

(D) $a + b = 2$

# 二、填空题(本题共6小题，每小题4分，共24分，把答案填在题中横线上.)', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第08题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第08题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第8题 (8) 设 $f_{1}(x)$ 为标准正态分布的概率密度, $f_{2}(x)$ 为 $[-1,3]$ 上均匀分布的概率密度, 若

$$
f (x) = \left\{ \begin{array}{l l} a f _ {1} (x), & x \leqslant 0, \\ b f _ {2} (x), & x > 0 \end{array} \right. (a > 0, b > 0)
$$

为概率密度, 则 $a, b$ 应满足( )

(a) $2a + 3b = 4$

(b) $3a + 2b = 4$

(c) $a + b = 1$

(d) $a + b = 2$

# 二、填空题(本题共6小题，每小题4分，共24分，把答案填在题中横线上.)');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q08', 'tag_概率');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q08', 'math1_2010_main_q08', 2010, 8, 8, 8, '（8）【答案】 （A）.

【解】 $f_{1}(x) = \frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}}\mathrm{e}^{-\frac{x^{2}}{2}}(-\infty < x < + \infty),\quad f_{2}(x) = \left\{ \begin{array}{ll}\frac{1}{4}, & -1\leqslant x\leqslant 3,\\ 0, & \text{其他}. \end{array} \right.$

因为 $f(x)$ 为概率密度函数，所以 $\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} f(x) \, \mathrm{d}x = 1$

而 $\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}f(x)\mathrm{d}x = a\int_{-\infty}^{0}f_{1}(x)\mathrm{d}x + b\int_{0}^{+\infty}f_{2}(x)\mathrm{d}x = \frac{a}{2} +b\int_{0}^{3}\frac{1}{4}\mathrm{d}x = \frac{a}{2} +\frac{3}{4} b,$

所以 $\frac{a}{2} +\frac{3}{4} b = 1$ ，即 $2a + 3b = 4$ ，应选（A）.

# 二、填空题', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.156, '2010:8', 8, 0.156);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q09', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 9, '(9) 设 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} x = \mathrm{e}^{-t}, \\ y = \int_{0}^{t} \ln (1 + u^{2}) \, \mathrm{d}u, \end{array} \right.$ 则 $\left. \frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2} \right|_{t=0} = \_$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第09题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第09题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第9题 (9) 设 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} x = \mathrm{e}^{-t}, \\ y = \int_{0}^{t} \ln (1 + u^{2}) \, \mathrm{d}u, \end{array} \right.$ 则 $\left. \frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2} \right|_{t=0} = \_$ .');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q09', 'tag_积分');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q09', 'math1_2010_main_q09', 2010, 9, 9, 9, '（9）【答案】0.

【解】 $\frac{\mathrm{dy}}{\mathrm{dx}} = \frac{\mathrm{dy} / \mathrm{dt}}{\mathrm{dx} / \mathrm{dt}} = -\mathrm{e}^{t}\ln (1 + t^{2}),$

$$
\begin{array}{l} \frac {\mathrm {d} ^ {2} y}{\mathrm {d} x ^ {2}} = \frac {\mathrm {d} \left(\frac {\mathrm {d} y}{\mathrm {d} x}\right) / \mathrm {d} t}{\mathrm {d} x / \mathrm {d} t} = - \left[ \mathrm {e} ^ {t} \ln (1 + t ^ {2}) + \mathrm {e} ^ {t} \frac {2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} \right] \cdot (- \mathrm {e} ^ {t}) \\ = \mathrm {e} ^ {2 t} \left[ \ln (1 + t ^ {2}) + \frac {2 t}{1 + t ^ {2}} \right], \\ \end{array}
$$

于是 $\left.\frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2}\right|_{t = 0} = 0.$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.357, '2010:9', 9, 0.357);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q10', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 10, '(10) $\int_{0}^{\pi^{2}} \sqrt{x} \cos \sqrt{x} \mathrm{d}x = \underline{\quad}$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第10题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第10题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第10题 (10) $\int_{0}^{\pi^{2}} \sqrt{x} \cos \sqrt{x} \mathrm{d}x = \underline{\quad}$ .');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q10', 'tag_积分');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q10', 'math1_2010_main_q10', 2010, 10, 10, 10, '（10）【答案】 $-4\pi$

【解】 $\int_0^{\pi^2}\sqrt{x}\cos \sqrt{x}\mathrm{d}x\stackrel {x = t^2}{= 2\int_0^\pi t^2\cos t\mathrm{d}t} = 2\int_0^\pi t^2\mathrm{d}(\sin t)$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = 2 t ^ {2} \sin t \left| _ {0} ^ {\pi} - 4 \int_ {0} ^ {\pi} t \sin t d t = - 4 \int_ {0} ^ {\pi} t \sin t d t \right. \\ = - 2 \pi \int_ {0} ^ {\pi} \sin t d t = - 4 \pi \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {\pi}{2}} \sin t d t = - 4 \pi . \\ \end{array}
$$

方法点评：本题考查定积分计算的方法和性质，

定积分计算主要使用两大工具，即定积分的性质及积分法。本题使用三角函数定积分性质，三角函数定积分的性质总结如下：

(1) $\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}} f(\sin x) \, \mathrm{d}x = \int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}} f(\cos x) \, \mathrm{d}x$ ，特别地，

$$
I _ {n} = \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {\pi}{2}} \sin^ {n} x \mathrm {d} x = \int_ {0} ^ {\frac {\pi}{2}} \cos^ {n} x \mathrm {d} x  , \text {且}   I _ {n} = \frac {n - 1}{n} I _ {n - 2}  , I _ {0} = \frac {\pi}{2}  , I _ {1} = 1.
$$

(2) $\int_{0}^{\pi} f(\sin x) \, \mathrm{d}x = 2\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}} f(\sin x) \, \mathrm{d}x$ ，或 $\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}} f(\sin x) \, \mathrm{d}x = \int_{\frac{\pi}{2}}^{\pi} f(\sin x) \, \mathrm{d}x$ .  
(3) $\int_{0}^{\pi} f(|\cos x|) \mathrm{d}x = 2 \int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}} f(\cos x) \mathrm{d}x.$   
(4) $\int_{0}^{\pi} x f(\sin x) \, \mathrm{d}x = \frac{\pi}{2} \int_{0}^{\pi} f(\sin x) \, \mathrm{d}x.$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.667, '2010:10', 4, 0.667);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q11', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 11, '(11)已知曲线 $L$ 的方程为 $y = 1 - |x|(x\in [-1,1])$ ，起点是 $(-1,0)$ ，终点为 $(1,0)$ ，则曲线积分 $\int_{L}xy\mathrm{d}x + x^{2}\mathrm{d}y = \underline{\quad}$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第11题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第11题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第11题 (11)已知曲线 $l$ 的方程为 $y = 1 - |x|(x\in [-1,1])$ ，起点是 $(-1,0)$ ，终点为 $(1,0)$ ，则曲线积分 $\int_{l}xy\mathrm{d}x + x^{2}\mathrm{d}y = \underline{\quad}$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q11', 'tag_积分');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q11', 'math1_2010_main_q11', 2010, 11, 11, 11, '（11）【答案】0.

【解】方法一 补充 $L_{1}:y = 0$ （起点 $(1,0)$ ，终点 $(-1,0))$ ，由格林公式

$$
\int_ {L} x y \mathrm {d} x + x ^ {2} \mathrm {d} y = \oint_ {L + L _ {1}} x y \mathrm {d} x + x ^ {2} \mathrm {d} y - \int_ {L _ {1}} x y \mathrm {d} x + x ^ {2} \mathrm {d} y,
$$

而 $\oint_{L + L_1}xy\mathrm{d}x + x^2\mathrm{d}y = \iint_Dx\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y = \int_0^1\mathrm{d}y\int_{y - 1}^{1 - y}x\mathrm{d}x = 0,$

$$
\int_ {L _ {1}} x y \mathrm {d} x + x ^ {2} \mathrm {d} y = \int_ {L _ {1}} x y \mathrm {d} x = 0,
$$

所以原式 $= 0$

方法二 $\int_{L} xy \, \mathrm{d}x + x^2 \, \mathrm{d}y = \int_{-1}^{0} [x(1 + x) + x^2] \, \mathrm{d}x + \int_{0}^{1} [x(1 - x) - x^2] \, \mathrm{d}x = 0.$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.256, '2010:11', 11, 0.256);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q12', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 12, '(12) 设 $\Omega = \{(x, y, z) \mid x^2 + y^2 \leqslant z \leqslant 1\}$ , 则 $\Omega$ 的形心的竖坐标 $\bar{z} = \_$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第12题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第12题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第12题 (12) 设 $\omega = \{(x, y, z) \mid x^2 + y^2 \leqslant z \leqslant 1\}$ , 则 $\omega$ 的形心的竖坐标 $\bar{z} = \_$ .');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q12', 'math1_2010_main_q12', 2010, 12, 12, 12, '(12)【答案】 $\frac{2}{3}$ .

【解】 方法一 $\overline{z} = \frac{\iiint_{\Omega} z \mathrm{d}v}{\iiint_{\Omega} \mathrm{d}v}$ ，而 $\iiint_{\Omega} z \mathrm{d}v = \int_{0}^{1} z \mathrm{d}z \iint_{x^2 + y^2 \leqslant z} \mathrm{d}x \mathrm{d}y = \pi \int_{0}^{1} z^2 \mathrm{d}z = \frac{\pi}{3}$

$$
\iiint_ {\Omega} \mathrm {d} v = \int_ {0} ^ {1} \mathrm {d} z \iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \leqslant z} \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y = \pi \int_ {0} ^ {1} z \mathrm {d} z = \frac {\pi}{2}, \text {所 以} \overline {{z}} = \frac {2}{3}.
$$

方法二 $\overline{z} = \frac{\iiint_{\Omega} z \mathrm{~d} v}{\iiint_{\Omega} \mathrm{~d} v}$ ,

由 $\Omega = \{(x,y,z)\mid (x,y)\in D_{xy},x^2 +y^2\leqslant z\leqslant 1\}$ ，其中 $D_{xy} = \{(x,y)|x^2 +y^2\leqslant 1\}$ 得

$$
\begin{array}{l} \iiint_ {\Omega} \mathrm {d} v = \iint_ {D _ {x y}} \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y \int_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}} ^ {1} \mathrm {d} z = \iint_ {D _ {x y}} (1 - x ^ {2} - y ^ {2}) \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y \\ = \int_ {0} ^ {2 \pi} d \theta \int_ {0} ^ {1} r (1 - r ^ {2}) d r = 2 \pi \int_ {0} ^ {1} (r - r ^ {3}) d r = 2 \pi \left(\frac {1}{2} - \frac {1}{4}\right) = \frac {\pi}{2}; \\ \end{array}
$$

$$
\begin{array}{l} \iiint_ {\Omega} z \mathrm {d} v = \iint_ {D _ {x y}} \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y \int_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}} ^ {1} z \mathrm {d} z = \frac {1}{2} \iint_ {D _ {x y}} [ 1 - (x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}) ^ {2} ] \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y \\ = \frac {1}{2} \int_ {0} ^ {2 \pi} \mathrm {d} \theta \int_ {0} ^ {1} r (1 - r ^ {4}) \mathrm {d} r = \pi \int_ {0} ^ {1} (r - r ^ {5}) \mathrm {d} r = \pi \left(\frac {1}{2} - \frac {1}{6}\right) = \frac {\pi}{3}, \\ \end{array}
$$

故 $\overline{z} = \frac{2}{3}$

方法点评：形心的计算是重积分及线和面积分的物理应用之一.

（1）设 $D$ 为平面有限区域，其面密度为 $\rho (x,y)$ ，则

$$
\bar {x} = \frac {\iint_ {D} x \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} \sigma}{\iint_ {D} \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} \sigma}, \quad \bar {y} = \frac {\iint_ {D} y \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} \sigma}{\iint_ {D} \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} \sigma}.
$$

（2）设 $\Omega$ 为空间有限区域，其体密度为 $\rho (x,y,z)$ ，则

$$
\bar {x} = \frac {\iiint_ {\Omega} x \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} v}{\iiint_ {\Omega} \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} v}, \quad \bar {y} = \frac {\iiint_ {\Omega} y \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} v}{\iiint_ {\Omega} \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} v}, \quad \bar {z} = \frac {\iiint_ {\Omega} z \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} v}{\iiint_ {\Omega} \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} v}.
$$

（3）设 $L$ 为平面有限曲线段，其线密度为 $\rho (x,y)$ ，则

$$
\bar {x} = \frac {\int_ {L} x \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} s}{\int_ {L} \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} s}, \quad \bar {y} = \frac {\int_ {L} y \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} s}{\int_ {L} \rho (x , y) \mathrm {d} s}.
$$

（4）设 $\Sigma$ 为空间有限曲面，其面密度为 $\rho (x,y,z)$ ，则

$$
\bar {x} = \frac {\iint_ {\Sigma} x \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} S}{\iint_ {\Sigma} \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} S}, \quad \bar {y} = \frac {\iint_ {\Sigma} y \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} S}{\iint_ {\Sigma} \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} S}, \quad \bar {z} = \frac {\iint_ {\Sigma} z \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} S}{\iint_ {\Sigma} \rho (x , y , z) \mathrm {d} S}.
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.421, '2010:12', 12, 0.421);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q13', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 13, '(13) 设 $\pmb{\alpha}_{1} = (1,2, - 1,0)^{\mathrm{T}},\pmb{\alpha}_{2} = (1,1,0,2)^{\mathrm{T}},\pmb{\alpha}_{3} = (2,1,1,a)^{\mathrm{T}}$ 若由 $\pmb{\alpha}_{1},\pmb{\alpha}_{2},\pmb{\alpha}_{3}$ 生成的向量空间的维数为2，则 $a =$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第13题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第13题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第13题 (13) 设 $\pmb{\alpha}_{1} = (1,2, - 1,0)^{\mathrm{t}},\pmb{\alpha}_{2} = (1,1,0,2)^{\mathrm{t}},\pmb{\alpha}_{3} = (2,1,1,a)^{\mathrm{t}}$ 若由 $\pmb{\alpha}_{1},\pmb{\alpha}_{2},\pmb{\alpha}_{3}$ 生成的向量空间的维数为2，则 $a =$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q13', 'tag_线性代数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q13', 'math1_2010_main_q13', 2010, 13, 13, 13, '（13）【答案】 6.

【解】 $(\pmb{\alpha}_{1},\pmb{\alpha}_{2},\pmb{\alpha}_{3}) = \begin{bmatrix} 1 & 1 & 2\\ 2 & 1 & 1\\ -1 & 0 & 1\\ 0 & 2 & a \end{bmatrix} \rightarrow \begin{bmatrix} 1 & 1 & 2\\ 0 & -1 & -3\\ 0 & 1 & 3\\ 0 & 2 & a \end{bmatrix} \rightarrow \begin{bmatrix} 1 & 1 & 2\\ 0 & 1 & 3\\ 0 & 0 & 0\\ 0 & 0 & a - 6 \end{bmatrix}$

因为由 $\alpha_{1},\alpha_{2},\alpha_{3}$ 组成的向量组的秩为2，所以 $a = 6$

方法点评：向量组的秩与向量组所构成的矩阵的秩相等，因为向量组 $\alpha_{1},\alpha_{2},\alpha_{3}$ 的秩为2，所以其构成的矩阵的秩为2，经过初等行变换阶梯化后应为2个非零行，故可求出 $a$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.216, '2010:13', 13, 0.216);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q14', 'math1', 2010, '真题', 'main', 14, '(14) 设随机变量 $X$ 的概率分布为 $P\{X = k\} = \frac{C}{k!}, k = 0,1,2,\dots,$ 则 $E(X^2) = \_$

# 三、解答题（本题共9小题，共94分，解答应写出文字说明、证明过程或演算步骤）', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\按题拆分\真题\第14题\题目.md', '2010\按题拆分\真题\第14题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2010 真题 第14题 (14) 设随机变量 $x$ 的概率分布为 $p\{x = k\} = \frac{c}{k!}, k = 0,1,2,\dots,$ 则 $e(x^2) = \_$

# 三、解答题（本题共9小题，共94分，解答应写出文字说明、证明过程或演算步骤）');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2010_main_q14', 'tag_概率');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2010_main_q14', 'math1_2010_main_q14', 2010, 14, 14, 14, '（14）【答案】2.

【解】方法一 由概率的归一性得 $1 = \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} \frac{C}{k!} = C \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} \frac{1}{k!} = C \mathrm{e}$ , 则 $C = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}}$

由 $P\{X = k\} = \frac{1}{k!}\mathrm{e}^{-1}(k = 0,1,2,\dots)$ 得 $X\sim P(1)$

于是 $E(X) = D(X) = 1$ ，故 $E(X^2) = D(X) + (EX)^2 = 2.$

方法二 由 $\sum_{k=0}^{\infty} \frac{C}{k!} = C \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} \frac{1}{k!} = C \mathrm{e} = 1$ 得 $C = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}}$

则 $E(X^{2}) = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}}\sum_{k = 0}^{\infty}\frac{k^{2}}{k!} = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}}\sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}\frac{k^{2}}{k!} = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}}\sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}\frac{k}{(k - 1)!} = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}}\sum_{k = 1}^{\infty}\frac{(k - 1) + 1}{(k - 1)!}$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = \frac {1}{\mathrm {e}} \sum_ {k = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {k - 1}{(k - 1) !} + \frac {1}{\mathrm {e}} \sum_ {k = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {1}{(k - 1) !} = \frac {1}{\mathrm {e}} \sum_ {k = 2} ^ {\infty} \frac {1}{(k - 2) !} + \frac {1}{\mathrm {e}} \sum_ {k = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {1}{(k - 1) !} \\ = 2. \\ \end{array}
$$

方法点评：随机变量的分布中若含有待定参数，则可以利用概率的归一性求出参数值.

# 三、解答题', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2010\解析\2010年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.179, '2010:14', 14, 0.179);
