设函数 $f(u)$ 具有二阶连续导数， $z = f(\mathrm{e}^{x}\cos y)$ 满足 $\frac{\partial^2 z}{\partial x^2} + \frac{\partial^2 z}{\partial y^2} = (4z + \mathrm{e}^x\cos y)\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ . 若 $f(0) = 0$ ， $f''(0) = 0$ ，求 $f(u)$ 的表达式.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2014\按题拆分\真题\第17题\题目.md', '2014\按题拆分\真题\第17题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2014 真题 第17题 (17)(本题满分10分)

设函数 $f(u)$ 具有二阶连续导数， $z = f(\mathrm{e}^{x}\cos y)$ 满足 $\frac{\partial^2 z}{\partial x^2} + \frac{\partial^2 z}{\partial y^2} = (4z + \mathrm{e}^x\cos y)\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ . 若 $f(0) = 0$ ， $f''(0) = 0$ ，求 $f(u)$ 的表达式.');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2014_main_q17', 'tag_连续');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2014_main_q17', 'tag_导数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2014_main_q17', 'math1_2014_main_q17', 2014, 17, 17, 17, '(17)【解】 $\frac{\partial z}{\partial x} = \mathrm{e}^{x}\cos y\cdot f^{\prime},\quad \frac{\partial z}{\partial y} = -\mathrm{e}^{x}\sin y\cdot f^{\prime},$

$$
\begin{array}{l} \frac {\partial^ {2} z}{\partial x ^ {2}} = \mathrm {e} ^ {x} \cos y \cdot f ^ {\prime} + \mathrm {e} ^ {2 x} \cos^ {2} y \cdot f ^ {\prime \prime}, \quad \frac {\partial^ {2} z}{\partial y ^ {2}} = - \mathrm {e} ^ {x} \cos y \cdot f ^ {\prime} + \mathrm {e} ^ {2 x} \sin^ {2} y \cdot f ^ {\prime \prime}, \\ \frac {\partial^ {2} z}{\partial x ^ {2}} + \frac {\partial^ {2} z}{\partial y ^ {2}} = \mathrm {e} ^ {2 x} f ^ {\prime \prime}, \\ \end{array}
$$

令 $u = \mathrm{e}^{x}\cos y$ ，由 $\frac{\partial^2z}{\partial x^2} +\frac{\partial^2z}{\partial y^2} = (4z + \mathrm{e}^x\cos y)\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ 得

$$
f ^ {\prime \prime} (u) = 4 f (u) + u \text {, 或} f ^ {\prime \prime} (u) - 4 f (u) = u
$$

解得 $f(u) = C_{1}\mathrm{e}^{-2u} + C_{2}\mathrm{e}^{2u} - \frac{1}{4} u$

由 $f(0) = 0, f''(0) = 0$ 得 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} C_1 + C_2 = 0, \\ -2C_1 + 2C_2 - \frac{1}{4} = 0, \end{array} \right.$ 解得 $C_1 = -\frac{1}{16}, C_2 = \frac{1}{16}$ ,

故 $f(u) = \frac{1}{16} (\mathrm{e}^{2u} - \mathrm{e}^{-2u}) - \frac{1}{4} u.$

方法点评：本题考查偏导数与二阶常系数非齐次线性微分方程

偏导数与微分方程结合问题是一种综合和重要的题型，首先按题目要求计算出相应的偏导数，根据给定的等量关系式将偏导数代入等式中，整理得微分方程，再根据微分方程的类型对微分方程求解.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2014\解析\2014年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.309, '2014:17', 17, 0.309);
