【解】 $\int_{0}^{+\infty}\frac{\mathrm{d}x}{x^2 + 2x + 2} = \int_{0}^{+\infty}\frac{\mathrm{d}(x + 1)}{1 + (x + 1)^2} = \arctan (x + 1)\mid_{0}^{+\infty} = \frac{\pi}{2} -\frac{\pi}{4} = \frac{\pi}{4}.$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.75, '2021:11', 11, 0.75);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q12', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 12, '(2) 设函数 $y = y(x)$ 由参数方程 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} x = 2\mathrm{e}^t + t + 1, \\ y = 4(t - 1)\mathrm{e}^t + t^2 \end{array} \right.$ 所确定，则 $\left. \frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2} \right|_{t=0} =$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第12题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第12题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第12题 (2) 设函数 $y = y(x)$ 由参数方程 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} x = 2\mathrm{e}^t + t + 1, \\ y = 4(t - 1)\mathrm{e}^t + t^2 \end{array} \right.$ 所确定，则 $\left. \frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2} \right|_{t=0} =$');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q12', 'math1_2021_main_q12', 2021, 12, 12, 11, '(12)【答案】 $\frac{2}{3}$ .

【解】 $\frac{\mathrm{dy}}{\mathrm{dx}} = \frac{\mathrm{dy} / \mathrm{dt}}{\mathrm{dx} / \mathrm{dt}} = \frac{4te^{t} + 2t}{2e^{t} + 1} = 2t, \frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{dx}^2} = \frac{\mathrm{d}(2t) / \mathrm{dt}}{\mathrm{dx} / \mathrm{dt}} = \frac{2}{2e^{t} + 1},$

则 $\frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}x^2}\bigg|_{t = 0} = \frac{2}{3}.$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.186, '2021:12', 12, 0.186);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q13', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 13, '(3) 欧拉方程 $x^{2}y^{\prime \prime} + xy^{\prime} - 4y = 0$ 满足条件 $y(1) = 1, y^{\prime}(1) = 2$ 的解为 $y =$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第13题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第13题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第13题 (3) 欧拉方程 $x^{2}y^{\prime \prime} + xy^{\prime} - 4y = 0$ 满足条件 $y(1) = 1, y^{\prime}(1) = 2$ 的解为 $y =$');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q13', 'math1_2021_main_q13', 2021, 13, 13, 12, '（13）【答案】 $x^{2}$

【解】 令 $x = \mathrm{e}^{t},D = \frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}t}$ ，则

$$
x y ^ {\prime} = D y, x ^ {2} y ^ {\prime \prime} = D (D - 1) y,
$$

代入欧拉方程得

$$
\frac {\mathrm {d} ^ {2} y}{\mathrm {d} t ^ {2}} - 4 y = 0,
$$

特征方程为 $\lambda^2 - 4 = 0$ ，特征根为 $\lambda_1 = -2, \lambda_2 = 2$

$\frac{\mathrm{d}^2y}{\mathrm{d}t^2} - 4y = 0$ 的通解为 $y = C_1\mathrm{e}^{-2t} + C_2\mathrm{e}^{2t}$ ，原方程的通解为

$$
y = \frac {C _ {1}}{x ^ {2}} + C _ {2} x ^ {2},
$$

由 $y(1) = 1, y''(1) = 2$ 得 $C_1 + C_2 = 1, -2C_1 + 2C_2 = 2$ ，解得 $C_1 = 0, C_2 = 1$ ，故 $y = x^2$ .

方法点评：形如

$$
x ^ {n} y ^ {(n)} + a _ {n - 1} x ^ {n - 1} y ^ {(n - 1)} + \dots + a _ {1} x y ^ {\prime} + a _ {0} y = f (x)
$$

的方程称为欧拉方程.

令 $x = \mathrm{e}^{t}$ ，则 $xy^{\prime} = Dy = \frac{\mathrm{dy}}{\mathrm{dt}},x^{2}y^{\prime \prime} = D(D - 1)y = \frac{\mathrm{d}^{2}y}{\mathrm{d}t^{2}} -\frac{\mathrm{dy}}{\mathrm{dt}},$

$$
x ^ {n} y ^ {(n)} = D (D - 1) \dots (D - n + 1) y,
$$

代入原方程得高阶常系数线性微分方程，求出其通解，再将 $t = \ln x$ 代入即可得原方程的通解.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.36, '2021:13', 13, 0.36);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q14', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 14, '4）设 $\Sigma$ 为空间区域 $\{(x,y,z) \mid x^2 + 4y^2 \leqslant 4, 0 \leqslant z \leqslant 2\}$ 表面的外侧，则曲面积分 $\iint_{\Sigma} x^2 \mathrm{d}y \mathrm{d}z + y^2 \mathrm{d}z \mathrm{d}x + z \mathrm{d}x \mathrm{d}y = \underline{\quad}$ .', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第14题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第14题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第14题 4）设 $\sigma$ 为空间区域 $\{(x,y,z) \mid x^2 + 4y^2 \leqslant 4, 0 \leqslant z \leqslant 2\}$ 表面的外侧，则曲面积分 $\iint_{\sigma} x^2 \mathrm{d}y \mathrm{d}z + y^2 \mathrm{d}z \mathrm{d}x + z \mathrm{d}x \mathrm{d}y = \underline{\quad}$ .');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q14', 'tag_积分');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q14', 'tag_多元函数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q14', 'math1_2021_main_q14', 2021, 14, 14, 13, '（14）【答案】 $4\pi$

【解】设 $\Sigma$ 所围成的几何体为 $\Omega$ ，由高斯公式得

$$
I = \iint_ {\Sigma} x ^ {2} \mathrm {d} y \mathrm {d} z + y ^ {2} \mathrm {d} z \mathrm {d} x + z \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y = \iiint_ {\Omega} (2 x + 2 y + 1) \mathrm {d} v,
$$

由积分的奇偶性得

$$
I = \iiint_ {\Omega} \mathrm {d} v = 2 \iint_ {D _ {x y}} \mathrm {d} x \mathrm {d} y = 2 \cdot \pi \cdot 1 \cdot 2 = 4 \pi .
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.326, '2021:14', 14, 0.326);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q15', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 15, '5）设 $\mathbf{A} = (a_{ij})$ 为3阶矩阵， $A_{ij}$ 为代数余子式，若 $\mathbf{A}$ 的每行元素之和均为2，且 $|\mathbf{A}| = 3$ 则 $A_{11} + A_{21} + A_{31} = \_$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第15题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第15题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第15题 5）设 $\mathbf{a} = (a_{ij})$ 为3阶矩阵， $a_{ij}$ 为代数余子式，若 $\mathbf{a}$ 的每行元素之和均为2，且 $|\mathbf{a}| = 3$ 则 $a_{11} + a_{21} + a_{31} = \_$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q15', 'tag_线性代数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q15', 'math1_2021_main_q15', 2021, 15, 15, 14, '(15)【答案】 $\frac{3}{2}$ .

【解】 $|\mathbf{A}| = 2\left| \begin{array}{lll}1 & a_{12} & a_{13}\\ 1 & a_{22} & a_{23}\\ 1 & a_{32} & a_{33} \end{array} \right| = 2(A_{11} + A_{21} + A_{31}) = 3$ ，则

$$
A _ {1 1} + A _ {2 1} + A _ {3 1} = \frac {3}{2}.
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.22, '2021:15', 15, 0.22);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q16', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 16, '(16) 甲、乙两个盒子中各装有 2 个红球和 2 个白球, 先从甲盒中任取一球, 观察颜色后放入乙盒中, 再从乙盒中任取一球, 令 $X, Y$ 分别表示从甲盒和乙盒中取到的红球个数, 则 $X$ 与 $Y$

的相关系数为

# 三、解答题（17～22小题，共70分.解答应写出文字说明、证明过程或演算步骤.）', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第16题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第16题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第16题 (16) 甲、乙两个盒子中各装有 2 个红球和 2 个白球, 先从甲盒中任取一球, 观察颜色后放入乙盒中, 再从乙盒中任取一球, 令 $x, y$ 分别表示从甲盒和乙盒中取到的红球个数, 则 $x$ 与 $y$

的相关系数为

# 三、解答题（17～22小题，共70分.解答应写出文字说明、证明过程或演算步骤.）');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q16', 'math1_2021_main_q16', 2021, 16, 16, 15, '(16)【答案】 $\frac{1}{5}$ .

【解】 $(X,Y)$ 的可能取值为 $(0,0),(0,1),(1,0),(1,1)$

$$
P \{X = 0, Y = 0 \} = \frac {1}{2} \cdot \frac {3}{5} = \frac {3}{1 0},
$$

$$
P \{X = 0, Y = 1 \} = \frac {1}{2} \cdot \frac {2}{5} = \frac {1}{5},
$$

$$
P \{X = 1, Y = 0 \} = \frac {1}{2} \cdot \frac {2}{5} = \frac {1}{5},
$$

$$
P \{X = 1, Y = 1 \} = \frac {1}{2} \cdot \frac {3}{5} = \frac {3}{1 0},
$$

由 $X \sim \left( \begin{array}{ll} 0 & 1 \\ \frac{1}{2} & \frac{1}{2} \end{array} \right)$ 得 $E(X) = \frac{1}{2}, E(X^2) = \frac{1}{2}, D(X) = \frac{1}{4}$ ;

由 $Y\sim \left( \begin{array}{ll}0 & 1\\ \frac{1}{2} & \frac{1}{2} \end{array} \right)$ 得 $E(Y) = \frac{1}{2},E(Y^2) = \frac{1}{2},D(Y) = \frac{1}{4};$

由 $XY \sim \left( \begin{array}{cc} 0 & 1 \\ \frac{7}{10} & \frac{3}{10} \end{array} \right)$ 得 $E(XY) = \frac{3}{10}$ ,

$\operatorname{Cov}(X,Y) = E(XY) - E(X)E(Y) = \frac{3}{10} - \frac{1}{4} = \frac{1}{20}$ ，则 $\rho_{XY} = \frac{\frac{1}{20}}{\frac{1}{2} \cdot \frac{1}{2}} = \frac{1}{5}$ .

# 三、解答题', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.019, '2021:16', 16, 0.019);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q17', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 17, '（17）（本题满分10分）

求极限 $\lim_{x\to 0}\left(\frac{1 + \int_{0}^{x}\mathrm{e}^{t^2}\mathrm{d}t}{\mathrm{e}^x - 1} -\frac{1}{\sin x}\right).$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第17题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第17题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第17题 （17）（本题满分10分）

求极限 $\lim_{x\to 0}\left(\frac{1 + \int_{0}^{x}\mathrm{e}^{t^2}\mathrm{d}t}{\mathrm{e}^x - 1} -\frac{1}{\sin x}\right).$');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q17', 'tag_极限');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q17', 'tag_积分');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q17', 'math1_2021_main_q17', 2021, 17, 17, 16, '（17）【解】 方法一

$$
\lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {1 + \int_ {0} ^ {x} \mathrm {e} ^ {t ^ {2}} \mathrm {d} t}{\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x}\right) = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\left(1 + \int_ {0} ^ {x} \mathrm {e} ^ {t ^ {2}} \mathrm {d} t\right) \sin x - \mathrm {e} ^ {x} + 1}{(\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1) \sin x}
$$

$$
\begin{array}{l} = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\left(1 + \int_ {0} ^ {x} e ^ {t ^ {2}} d t\right) \sin x - e ^ {x} + 1}{x ^ {2}} \\ = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {\sin x - x}{x ^ {2}} + \frac {\int_ {0} ^ {x} e ^ {t ^ {2}} d t \cdot \sin x - e ^ {x} + 1 + x}{x ^ {2}}\right) \\ = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\int_ {0} ^ {x} e ^ {t ^ {2}} d t \cdot \sin x - e ^ {x} + 1 + x}{x ^ {2}} \\ = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\sin x}{x} \cdot \frac {\int_ {0} ^ {x} \mathrm {e} ^ {t ^ {2}} \mathrm {d} t}{x} - \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1 - x}{x ^ {2}} \\ = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \mathrm {e} ^ {x ^ {2}} - \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1}{2 x} = 1 - \frac {1}{2} = \frac {1}{2}. \\ \end{array}
$$

方法二

$$
\lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {1 + \int_ {0} ^ {x} e ^ {t ^ {2}} d t}{e ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x}\right) = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {\int_ {0} ^ {x} e ^ {t ^ {2}} d t}{e ^ {x} - 1} + \frac {1}{e ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x}\right),
$$

由 $\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{\int_{0}^{x}\mathrm{e}^{t^2}\mathrm{d}t}{\mathrm{e}^x - 1} = \lim_{x\to 0}\frac{\mathrm{e}^{x^2}}{\mathrm{e}^x} = 1,$

$$
\begin{array}{l} \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {1}{\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x}\right) = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\sin x - \mathrm {e} ^ {x} + 1}{(\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1) \sin x} = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\sin x - \mathrm {e} ^ {x} + 1}{x ^ {2}} \\ = \frac {1}{2} \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\cos x - e ^ {x}}{x} = \frac {1}{2} \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} (- \sin x - e ^ {x}) = - \frac {1}{2}, \\ \end{array}
$$

得 $\lim_{x\to 0}\left(\frac{1 + \int_0^x\mathrm{e}^{t^2}\mathrm{d}t}{\mathrm{e}^x - 1} -\frac{1}{\sin x}\right) = 1 - \frac{1}{2} = \frac{1}{2}.$

方法三

由泰勒公式得 $\mathrm{e}^{t^2} = 1 + t^2 + o(t^2)$

从而 $\int_0^x\mathrm{e}^{t^2}\mathrm{d}t = x + \frac{x^3}{3} +o(x^3)$ ，于是有

$$
\begin{array}{l} \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {1 + \int_ {0} ^ {x} \mathrm {e} ^ {t ^ {2}} \mathrm {d} t}{\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x}\right) = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left[ \frac {1 + x + \frac {x ^ {3}}{3} + o \left(x ^ {3}\right)}{\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x} \right] = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {1 + x}{\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x}\right) \\ = \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {x}{\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \left(\frac {1}{\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \frac {1}{\sin x}\right) \\ = 1 + \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\sin x - e ^ {x} + 1}{\left(e ^ {x} - 1\right) \sin x} = 1 + \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\sin x - e ^ {x} + 1}{x ^ {2}} \\ = 1 + \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {\cos x - e ^ {x}}{2 x} = 1 + \lim  _ {x \rightarrow 0} \frac {- \sin x - e ^ {x}}{2} = \frac {1}{2}. \\ \end{array}
$$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.52, '2021:17', 17, 0.52);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q18', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 18, '（18）（本题满分12分）

设 $u_{n}(x) = \mathrm{e}^{-nx} + \frac{x^{n + 1}}{n(n + 1)} (n = 1,2,\dots)$ ，求级数 $\sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}u_n(x)$ 的收敛域及和函数.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第18题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第18题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第18题 （18）（本题满分12分）

设 $u_{n}(x) = \mathrm{e}^{-nx} + \frac{x^{n + 1}}{n(n + 1)} (n = 1,2,\dots)$ ，求级数 $\sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}u_n(x)$ 的收敛域及和函数.');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO question_tags(question_id, tag_id) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q18', 'tag_级数');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q18', 'math1_2021_main_q18', 2021, 18, 18, 17, '(18)【解】 $\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} u_n(x) = \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \mathrm{e}^{-nx} + \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{x^{n+1}}{n(n+1)}$ ,

当 $\lim_{n\to \infty}\frac{\mathrm{e}^{-(n + 1)x}}{\mathrm{e}^{-nx}} = \mathrm{e}^{-x} <   1$ 即 $x > 0$ 时， $\sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}\mathrm{e}^{-nx}$ 收敛；

再由 $\lim_{n\to \infty}\frac{\frac{1}{(n + 1)(n + 2)}}{\frac{1}{n(n + 1)}} = 1$ 得 $\sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}\frac{x^{n + 1}}{n(n + 1)}$ 的收敛半径为 $R = 1$

当 $x = \pm 1$ 时， $\sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}\left|\frac{(\pm 1)^{n + 1}}{n(n + 1)}\right| = \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n(n + 1)} = 1$ 故 $\sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}\frac{x^{n + 1}}{n(n + 1)}$ 的收敛域为[-1,1]，故级数 $\sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}u_n(x)$ 的收敛域为(0,1].

令 $S(x) = \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} u_n(x) = \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \mathrm{e}^{-nx} + \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{x^{n+1}}{n(n+1)} = S_1(x) + S_2(x)$ ，

且 $S_{1}(x) = \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}\mathrm{e}^{-nx} = \frac{\mathrm{e}^{-x}}{1 - \mathrm{e}^{-x}} = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}^{x} - 1};$

$$
\begin{array}{l} S _ {2} (x) = \sum_ {n = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {x ^ {n + 1}}{n (n + 1)} = \sum_ {n = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {x ^ {n + 1}}{n} - \sum_ {n = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {x ^ {n + 1}}{n + 1} = x \sum_ {n = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {x ^ {n}}{n} - \sum_ {n = 1} ^ {\infty} \frac {x ^ {n}}{n} + x \\ = (1 - x) \ln (1 - x) + x (0 <   x <   1), \\ \end{array}
$$

当 $x = 1$ 时，由 $S_{1}(1) = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e} - 1}, S_{2}(1) = 1$ 得 $S(1) = \frac{1}{\mathrm{e} - 1} + 1 = \frac{\mathrm{e}}{\mathrm{e} - 1}$ ，

故 $S(x) = \left\{ \begin{array}{ll} \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}^x - 1} + (1 - x)\ln (1 - x) + x, & 0 < x < 1, \\ \frac{\mathrm{e}}{\mathrm{e} - 1}, & x = 1. \end{array} \right.$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.459, '2021:18', 18, 0.459);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q19', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 19, '（19）（本题满分12分）

已知曲线 $C: \left\{ \begin{array}{l} x^2 + 2y^2 - z = 6, \\ 4x + 2y + z = 30, \end{array} \right.$ 求 $C$ 上的点到 $xOy$ 坐标面距离的最大值.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第19题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第19题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第19题 （19）（本题满分12分）

已知曲线 $c: \left\{ \begin{array}{l} x^2 + 2y^2 - z = 6, \\ 4x + 2y + z = 30, \end{array} \right.$ 求 $c$ 上的点到 $xoy$ 坐标面距离的最大值.');
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO solutions(solution_id, question_id, year, question_no, chunk_no, source_chunk_index, content_md, source_path, quality_status, map_method, match_score, direct_key, best_chunk_no, best_score) VALUES ('sol_math1_2021_main_q19', 'math1_2021_main_q19', 2021, 19, 19, 18, '(19)【解】设 $M(x,y,z)\in C$ ，点 $M$ 到 $xOy$ 坐标面的距离 $d = |z|$

令 $F = z^2 + \lambda (x^2 + 2y^2 - z - 6) + \mu (4x + 2y + z - 30)$ ，

$\begin{cases} F_{x}^{\prime} = 2\lambda x + 4\mu = 0,\\ F_{y}^{\prime} = 4\lambda y + 2\mu = 0,\\ F_{z}^{\prime} = 2z - \lambda +\mu = 0,\\ F_{\lambda}^{\prime} = x^{2} + 2y^{2} - z - 6 = 0,\\ F_{\mu}^{\prime} = 4x + 2y + z - 30 = 0 \end{cases}$ 得 $\begin{cases} x = 4, \\ y = 1, \\ z = 12, \\ z = 66, \end{cases}$

故 $C$ 上的点 $(-8, -2, 66)$ 到 $xOy$ 面的距离最大为 66.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\解析\2021年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.365, '2021:19', 19, 0.365);
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO questions(question_id, subject_id, year, paper, paper_slug, question_no, content_md, source_path, relative_source_path, has_assets, quality_status, search_text) VALUES ('math1_2021_main_q20', 'math1', 2021, '真题', 'main', 20, '（20）（本题满分12分）

设 $D \subset \mathbf{R}^2$ 是有界单连通闭区域， $I(D) = \iint_{D} (4 - x^2 - y^2) \, \mathrm{d}x \, \mathrm{d}y$ 取得最大值的积分区域为 $D_1$ .

（I）求 $I(D_{1})$ 的值；  
（Ⅱ）计算 $\int_{\partial D_1} \frac{(x \mathrm{e}^{x^2 + 4y^2} + y) \mathrm{d}x + (4y \mathrm{e}^{x^2 + 4y^2} - x) \mathrm{d}y}{x^2 + 4y^2}$ ，其中 $\partial D_1$ 是 $D_1$ 的正向边界.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2021\按题拆分\真题\第20题\题目.md', '2021\按题拆分\真题\第20题\题目.md', 0, 'ok', '2021 真题 第20题 （20）（本题满分12分）

设 $d \subset \mathbf{r}^2$ 是有界单连通闭区域， $i(d) = \iint_{d} (4 - x^2 - y^2) \, \mathrm{d}x \, \mathrm{d}y$ 取得最大值的积分区域为 $d_1$ .

（i）求 $i(d_{1})$ 的值；  
（ⅱ）计算 $\int_{\partial d_1} \frac{(x \mathrm{e}^{x^2 + 4y^2} + y) \mathrm{d}x + (4y \mathrm{e}^{x^2 + 4y^2} - x) \mathrm{d}y}{x^2 + 4y^2}$ ，其中 $\partial d_1$ 是 $d_1$ 的正向边界.');
