$$
\bar {X} = \frac {1}{n} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} X _ {i}, \bar {Y} = \frac {1}{m} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {m} Y _ {i}, S _ {1} ^ {2} = \frac {1}{n - 1} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} \left(X _ {i} - \bar {X}\right) ^ {2}, S _ {2} ^ {2} = \frac {1}{m - 1} \sum_ {i = 1} ^ {m} \left(Y _ {i} - \bar {Y}\right) ^ {2}
$$

则( )

A.   
