若 $\gamma^T\alpha_i = \beta^T\alpha_i(i = 1,2,3)$ ，则 $k_{1}^{2} + k_{2}^{2} + k_{3}^{2} =$', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2023\按题拆分\真题\第15题\题目.md', '2023\按题拆分\真题\第15题\题目.md', 0, 'manual_check', '2023 真题 第15题 (15) 已知向量 $\alpha_{1} = \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 0 \\ 1 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}, \alpha_{2} = \begin{pmatrix} -1 \\ -1 \\ 0 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}, \alpha_{3} = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ 1 \\ -1 \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}, \beta = \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 1 \\ 1 \\ -1 \end{pmatrix}, \gamma = k_{1}\alpha_{1} + k_{2}\alpha_{2} + k_{3}\alpha_{3}$ ,

若 $\gamma^t\alpha_i = \beta^t\alpha_i(i = 1,2,3)$ ，则 $k_{1}^{2} + k_{2}^{2} + k_{3}^{2} =$');
