求函数 $f(x,y) = (y - x^2)(y - x^3)$ 的极值.

【解析】 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} f_{x}^{\prime} = -x(2y + 3xy - 5x^{3}) = 0 \\ f_{y}^{\prime} = 2y - x^{2} - x^{3} = 0 \end{array} \right.$ ，得驻点为(0,0)，(1,1)， $(\frac{2}{3},\frac{10}{27})$

$$
f _ {x x} ^ {\prime \prime} = - (2 y + 3 x y - 5 x ^ {3}) - x (3 y - 1 5 x ^ {2}), f _ {x y} ^ {\prime \prime} = - x (2 + 3 x), \quad f _ {y y} ^ {\prime \prime} = 2.
$$

代入 $(0,0)$ ， $\left\{ \begin{array}{l} A = f_{xx}^{\prime \prime} = 0 \\ B = f_{xy}^{\prime \prime} = 0 \\ C = f_{yy}^{\prime \prime} = 2 \end{array} \right.$ ，则 $AC - B^{2} = 0$ ，故充分条件失效，当 $x \to 0$ 时，取

$$
y = x ^ {2} + k x ^ {3} (k > 0), \quad f (x, y) = (y - x ^ {2}) (y - x ^ {3}) = k x ^ {3} [ x ^ {2} + (k - 1) x ^ {3} ] = k x ^ {5} + o (x ^ {5}),
$$

则 $\lim_{x\to 0}\frac{f(x,y)}{x^5} = \lim_{x\to 0}\frac{kx^5 + o(x^5)}{x^5} = k > 0$ ，由极限的局部保号性：存在 $\delta >0$ ，当 $x\in (-\delta ,0)$ 时， $\frac{f(x,y)}{x^5} >0$ ， $f(x,y) <   0 = f(0,0)$ ，当 $x\in (0,\delta)$ 时， $\frac{f(x,y)}{x^5} >0$ ， $f(x,y) > 0 = f(0,0)$ ，故(0,0)不是极值点；

代入(1,1)， $\left\{ \begin{array}{l}A = f_{xx}^{\prime \prime} = 12\\ B = f_{xy}^{\prime \prime} = -5\\ C = f_{yy}^{\prime \prime} = 2 \end{array} \right.$ 则 $AC - B^{2} <   0$ ，故(1,1)不是极值点；

代入 $(\frac{2}{3},\frac{10}{27})$ 的 $\left\{ \begin{array}{l}A = f_{xx}^{\prime \prime} = \frac{100}{27}\\ B = f_{xy}^{\prime \prime} = -\frac{8}{3}\\ C = f_{yy}^{\prime \prime} = 2 \end{array} \right.$ 则 $AC - B^{2} > 0$ 且 $A > 0$ ，故 $(\frac{2}{3},\frac{10}{27})$ 是极小值点；故 $f(\frac{2}{3},\frac{10}{27}) = -\frac{4}{729}$ 为极小值.', 'E:\数学自用\数据资料\真题\按年份整理\2023\解析\2023年解析.md', 'ok', 'year_question_no', 0.513, '2023:18', 18, 0.513);
