\left| (- 1) ^ {n} \right| \frac {1}{\sqrt [ 2 ]{n ^ {3}}} - \tan \left. \frac {1}{\sqrt [ 3 ]{n ^ {2}}}\right) \Bigg | = \left| - \frac {1}{3} \frac {1}{n ^ {2}} + o \left(\frac {1}{n ^ {2}}\right) \right|.
